snippet.title: Best VGM 2043 - Katamari Forever - Cherry Blossom Color Season (fanfare mix)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS3
Katamari Forever (2009)
Cherry Blossom Color Season (fanfare mix)
Beautiful Hummingbird
